text: CHD may refer to: ==Medicine== * Congenital heart defect * Coronary heart disease ==Organizations== * Church and Dwight, US household product manufacturer, NYSE symbol ==Transportation== * Russian Air Force, ICAO code * Chesterfield railway station, England, National Rail code * Chandler Municipal Airport, Arizona, USA, FAA LID ==Technology== * Compressed Hunks of Data, a file format used by the MAME emulator ==Other== * Chicago Hittite Dictionary, Oriental Institute of the University of Chicago
title: CHD
